data.description: Investors and all in between come see this jewel in the heart of the beautiful subdivision of Cottonade. Close to shopping, dining and 3 minutes from Ft. Liberty. This home includes 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. However; the features that really make this property a true gem is that includes a pool as well as a finished basement within feet of the pool (perfect for various ideas). Also this home has a lighted crawl space, 2 water spickets for the front and backyard, advanced security system with integrated air control and smoke/ carbon dioxide detectors, 2 sky lights, one for the kitchen and one in the dining room, in house laundry and recently rebuilt central AC unit. This home is a must see. Make an appointment today!
